(F. Morawitz)
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BC717108E5FFFF8DE8EF89CFA1EE95A" blockId="6.[151,1437,1407,1873]" box="[151,1436,1851,1873]" pageId="6" pageNumber="435">
<keyLead id="3089B4258E5FFFF8DE8EF89CFA1EE95A" box="[151,1436,1851,1873]" pageId="6" pageNumber="435">
- Flagellomere I 1.5 × as long as wide, II not longer than III................................. 
<taxonomicName id="4C786C938E5FFFF8DAB9F89BFA1EE95A" authority="(Fabricius)" baseAuthorityName="Fabricius" baseAuthorityYear="1775" box="[1184,1436,1851,1873]" class="Insecta" family="Crabronidae" genus="Lestica" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="435" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subterranea">
